# ğŸ§­ Traveling Trader System â€“ Design Document

## ğŸ¯ Overview
This system introduces a **Traveling Trader** to your DayZ server using **Expansion Market** and **Expansion Map** modules. The trader appears at random across multiple locations, with dynamic map markers and timed visibility.

## ğŸ› ï¸ Core Features

| Feature                          | Description |
|----------------------------------|-------------|
| â± Timed trader spawn/despawn     | Trader appears every 60 minutes |
| ğŸŒ Loads `.map` files             | Custom environments per trader location |
| ğŸ“ Dynamic map marker             | Marker appears when trader arrives |
| ğŸ•’ Marker lifetime                | Marker disappears after 30 minutes |
| ğŸ” No repeat locations            | Avoids repeating the last spot |
| ğŸ“¢ Player notifications           | Chat notification when trader arrives |

## ğŸ“‚ Folder Structure Example

```
missions/
